title: Frankenstein
source_genre: Classic Fiction; Gothic & Horror; Science Fiction
cover_description: A graphic print of large repeated anatomical hearts adorns this purple clothbound cover. The title of "Frankenstein" sits at the top center of the book cover, with the author's name "Mary Shelley" printed at the bottom center of the cover. The anatomical heart pattern leaves blank spaces at the top and bottom for the text readability.
